我来应付山姆大叔
I'll handle Uncle Sam.

177
00:20:49,110 --> 00:20:52,820
一个很像擎天柱的人把你打趴下了
So, how weird was it to see someone who looked exactly like Optimus

178
00:20:52,920 --> 00:20:54,480
这是多么诡异的一件事啊？
kicking the scrap out of you?

179
00:20:55,520 --> 00:20:57,650
